  <li>See also:  <a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2024/03/13/macos-sonoma-14-4-usb-hub-issues-reported/">MacRumors: macOS Sonoma 14.4 Causing USB Hub Issues for Some Users</a></li>
</ul>

